3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper introduces a power model and studies the conditions for minimizing area power consumption, which are topics related to systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper mentions coping with increasing data traffic demand, which could involve multimedia content. 
5. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper discusses caching users' content locally at the edge of the network, which could involve distributed computing.
